trans-unit.source: Provides <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject" /> objects with CodeDOM serialization services.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona los servicios de serialización de CodeDOM a los objetos <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject" />.

trans-unit.source: This is the base class from which other CodeDOM serializers, such as the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.ActivityCodeDomSerializer" />, are inherited.
trans-unit.target: Ésta es la clase base de la que se heredan otros serializadores de CodeDOM, como <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.ActivityCodeDomSerializer" />.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.DependencyObjectCodeDomSerializer> controls the generation of component initialization code for the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject> class at design time.
trans-unit.target: Controla <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.DependencyObjectCodeDomSerializer> la generación de código de inicialización de componente para la clase <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject> en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.DependencyObjectCodeDomSerializer" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.DependencyObjectCodeDomSerializer" />.

trans-unit.source: The serialization manager to use during serialization.
trans-unit.target: Administrador de serialización que se va a utilizar durante la serialización.
<see cref="T:System.Object" /> que se va a serializar.

trans-unit.source: Serializes the specified object into a CodeDOM object.
trans-unit.target: Serializa el objeto especificado en un objeto CodeDOM.

trans-unit.source: A CodeDOM object that represents the object that has been serialized.
trans-unit.target: Objeto CodeDOM que representa el objeto que se ha serializado.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="manager" /> or <paramref name="obj" /> contains a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="manager" /> o <paramref name="obj" /> contiene una referencia nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="obj" /> cannot be converted to a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="obj" /> no se puede convertir en <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject" />.
